```plantuml
@startuml DJMcK_aws-lake-training

actor User
participant "FDA S3 Bucket" as FDAS3
participant "AWS S3 Raw Zone" as RawS3
participant "AWS S3 Landing Zone" as LandingS3
participant "AWS S3 Curated Zone" as CuratedS3
participant "AWS EMR (Spark)" as EMR
participant "AWS Glue" as Glue
participant "AWS Athena" as Athena
participant "AWS Lambda" as Lambda
participant "AWS Step Functions" as StepFunctions
participant "AWS Comprehend Medical" as Comprehend

User -> FDAS3: Request Data
FDAS3 -> RawS3: Transfer Raw Data

RawS3 -> EMR: Trigger Data Transformation
EMR -> LandingS3: Store Transformed Data

LandingS3 -> EMR: Trigger Data Curation
EMR -> CuratedS3: Store Curated Data

CuratedS3 -> Glue: Metadata Catalog Update

User -> Athena: Query Data
Athena -> User: Return Query Results

CuratedS3 -> Lambda: Trigger Indications Extraction
Lambda -> StepFunctions: Start Workflow

StepFunctions -> Lambda: Invoke configure_count.py
Lambda -> Comprehend: Extract Medical Entities

Comprehend -> CuratedS3: Store Extracted Entities
CuratedS3 -> Lambda: Invoke query_athena.py
Lambda -> Athena: Query Indications

Athena -> Lambda: Return Indications
StepFunctions -> Lambda: Invoke iterator.py
Lambda -> StepFunctions: Determine Iteration Need

StepFunctions -> Lambda: Complete Workflow
Lambda -> User: Notify Completion

@enduml
```